        public UploadOptions.Builder overrideFile(boolean overrideFile)
        Sets overrideFile option.

        If overrideFile is TRUE files with the same name with be overridden on the server. This controls the api parameter renameifexists.

        For more details see here

        Parameters:
        overrideFile - true to override existing files with same name, false otherwise

        public UploadOptions.Builder partialUpload(boolean partialUpload)
